name: none
script: mkdir -p /mnt/zfs/mount -t nfs singlefs1-fileserver:/testzfs /mnt/zfs//usr/local/bin/python2.7 /home/cmelton/DynamicDiskCloudSoftware/Worker/GsutilWrapper.py --C 'gsutil|-q|cp|gs://gbsc-gcp-lab-snyder-users-cmelton/MakeIntervalList.py|./' --F './MakeIntervalList.py'python ./MakeIntervalList.py --F interval.interval_list --C '$JOBMULTNODASH'java -Xmx2g -Djava.io.tmpdir=/mnt/zfs/ -jar /home/cmelton/Software/GenomeAnalysisTK.jar -T RealignerTargetCreator -R /mnt/zfs/g1k_v37_decoy_ref/human_g1k_v37_decoy.fasta -I /mnt/zfs/cancer.sorted.dedup.bam -I /mnt/zfs/normal.sorted.dedup.bam -known /mnt/zfs/1000G_phase1.indels.b37.vcf -known /mnt/zfs/Mills_and_1000G_gold_standard.indels.b37.vcf -o /mnt/zfs/GATKRealignTargets.intervals -nt 4 -L interval.interval_list/usr/local/bin/python2.7 /home/cmelton/DynamicDiskCloudSoftware/Worker/GsutilWrapper.py --C 'gsutil|-q|cp|gs://gbsc-gcp-lab-snyder-users-cmelton/MakeNWayOutFile.py|/home/cmelton/Software/' --F '/home/cmelton/Software/MakeNWayOutFile.py'python /home/cmelton/Software/MakeNWayOutFile.py --I cancer.sorted.dedup.bam --J /mnt/zfs/cancer.sorted.dedup.realigned.bam --K normal.sorted.dedup.bam --L /mnt/zfs/normal.sorted.dedup.realigned.bam --F /mnt/zfs/nwayout.map

script: mkdir -p /mnt/zfs/mount -t nfs singlefs1-fileserver:/testzfs /mnt/zfs//usr/local/bin/python2.7 /home/cmelton/DynamicDiskCloudSoftware/Worker/GsutilWrapper.py --C 'gsutil|-q|cp|gs://gbsc-gcp-lab-snyder-users-cmelton/MakeIntervalList.py|./' --F './MakeIntervalList.py'python ./MakeIntervalList.py --F interval.interval_list --C '$JOBMULTNODASH'java -Xmx4g -Djava.io.tmpdir=/mnt/zfs -jar /home/cmelton/Software/GenomeAnalysisTK.jar -T BaseRecalibrator -dcov 2 -R /mnt/zfs/g1k_v37_decoy_ref/human_g1k_v37_decoy.fasta -I /mnt/zfs/cancer.sorted.dedup.realigned.bam -knownSites /mnt/zfs/dbsnp_138.b37.vcf -knownSites /mnt/zfs/hapmap_3.3.b37.vcf -o /mnt/zfs/$JOBID/cancer.sorted.dedup.realigned.recalData.grp -nct 4 -L interval.interval_listjava -Xmx8g -Djava.io.tmpdir=/mnt/zfs -jar /home/cmelton/Software/GenomeAnalysisTK.jar -T PrintReads -R /mnt/zfs/g1k_v37_decoy_ref/human_g1k_v37_decoy.fasta -I /mnt/zfs/$JOBID/cancer.sorted.dedup.realigned.bam -BQSR /mnt/zfs/$JOBID/cancer.sorted.dedup.realigned.recalData.grp -o /mnt/zfs/$JOBID/cancer.sorted.dedup.realigned.recal.bam -nct 4 -rf BadCigar

script: mkdir -p /mnt/zfs/mount -t nfs singlefs1-fileserver:/testzfs /mnt/zfs/mkdir -p /mnt/zfs/$JOBID/usr/local/bin/python2.7 /home/cmelton/DynamicDiskCloudSoftware/Worker/GsutilWrapper.py --C 'gsutil|-q|cp|gs://gbsc-gcp-lab-snyder-users-cmelton/MakeIntervalList.py|./' --F './MakeIntervalList.py'python ./MakeIntervalList.py --F interval.interval_list --C '$JOBMULTNODASH'java -Xmx2g -Djava.io.tmpdir=/mnt/zfs/$JOBID/ -jar /home/cmelton/Software/GenomeAnalysisTK.jar -T RealignerTargetCreator -R /mnt/zfs/g1k_v37_decoy_ref/human_g1k_v37_decoy.fasta -I /mnt/zfs/cancer.sorted.dedup.bam -I /mnt/zfs/normal.sorted.dedup.bam -known /mnt/zfs/1000G_phase1.indels.b37.vcf -known /mnt/zfs/Mills_and_1000G_gold_standard.indels.b37.vcf -o /mnt/zfs/$JOBID/GATKRealignTargets.intervals -nt 4 -L interval.interval_list/usr/local/bin/python2.7 /home/cmelton/DynamicDiskCloudSoftware/Worker/GsutilWrapper.py --C 'gsutil|-q|cp|gs://gbsc-gcp-lab-snyder-users-cmelton/MakeNWayOutFile.py|/home/cmelton/Software/' --F '/home/cmelton/Software/MakeNWayOutFile.py'python /home/cmelton/Software/MakeNWayOutFile.py --I cancer.sorted.dedup.bam --J /mnt/zfs/$JOBID/cancer.sorted.dedup.realigned.bam --K normal.sorted.dedup.bam --L /mnt/zfs/$JOBID/normal.sorted.dedup.realigned.bam --F /mnt/zfs/$JOBID/nwayout.map

script: mkdir -p /mnt/zfs/mount -t nfs singlefs1-fileserver:/testzfs /mnt/zfs//usr/local/bin/python2.7 /home/cmelton/DynamicDiskCloudSoftware/Worker/GsutilWrapper.py --C 'gsutil|-q|cp|gs://gbsc-gcp-lab-snyder-users-cmelton/MakeIntervalList.py|./' --F './MakeIntervalList.py'python ./MakeIntervalList.py --F interval.interval_list --C '$JOBMULTNODASH'java -Xmx2g -Djava.io.tmpdir=/mnt/zfs/$JOBID/ -jar /home/cmelton/Software/GenomeAnalysisTK.jar -T IndelRealigner -R /mnt/zfs/g1k_v37_decoy_ref/human_g1k_v37_decoy.fasta -I /mnt/zfs/cancer.sorted.dedup.bam -I /mnt/zfs/normal.sorted.dedup.bam -known /mnt/zfs/1000G_phase1.indels.b37.vcf -known /mnt/zfs/Mills_and_1000G_gold_standard.indels.b37.vcf -targetIntervals /mnt/zfs/$JOBID/GATKRealignTargets.intervals -nWayOut /mnt/zfs/$JOBID/nwayout.map -L interval.interval_list

name: $JOBIDnode$JOBMULT-cancer-recal
script: mkdir -p /mnt/zfs/mount -t nfs singlefs1-fileserver:/testzfs /mnt/zfs//usr/local/bin/python2.7 /home/cmelton/DynamicDiskCloudSoftware/Worker/GsutilWrapper.py --C 'gsutil|-q|cp|gs://gbsc-gcp-lab-snyder-users-cmelton/MakeIntervalList.py|./' --F './MakeIntervalList.py'python ./MakeIntervalList.py --F interval.interval_list --C '$JOBMULTNODASH'java -Xmx4g -Djava.io.tmpdir=/mnt/zfs -jar /home/cmelton/Software/GenomeAnalysisTK.jar -T BaseRecalibrator -dcov 2 -R /mnt/zfs/g1k_v37_decoy_ref/human_g1k_v37_decoy.fasta -I /mnt/zfs/cancer.sorted.dedup.realigned.bam -knownSites /mnt/zfs/dbsnp_138.b37.vcf -knownSites /mnt/zfs/hapmap_3.3.b37.vcf -o /mnt/zfs/$JOBID/cancer.sorted.dedup.realigned.recalData.grp -nct 4 -L interval.interval_listjava -Xmx8g -Djava.io.tmpdir=/mnt/zfs -jar /home/cmelton/Software/GenomeAnalysisTK.jar -T PrintReads -R /mnt/zfs/g1k_v37_decoy_ref/human_g1k_v37_decoy.fasta -I /mnt/zfs/$JOBID/cancer.sorted.dedup.realigned.bam -BQSR /mnt/zfs/$JOBID/cancer.sorted.dedup.realigned.recalData.grp -o /mnt/zfs/$JOBID/cancer.sorted.dedup.realigned.recal.bam -nct 4 -rf BadCigar

name: $JOBIDnode$JOBMULT-mutect
script: mkdir -p /mnt/zfs/mount -t nfs singlefs1-fileserver:/testzfs /mnt/zfs//usr/lib/jvm/jre-1.6.0/bin/java -Xmx2g -Djava.io.tmpdir=/mnt/zfs -jar /home/cmelton/Software/muTect-1.1.1.jar --analysis_type MuTect --reference_sequence /mnt/zfs/g1k_v37_decoy_ref/human_g1k_v37_decoy.fasta --cosmic /mnt/zfs/b37_cosmic_v54_120711.vcf --dbsnp /mnt/zfs/dbsnp_132_b37.leftAligned.vcf --input_file:normal /mnt/zfs/$JOBID/normal.sorted.dedup.realigned.recal.bam --input_file:tumor /mnt/zfs/$JOBID/cancer.sorted.dedup.realigned.recal.bam --out /mnt/zfs/$JOBID/$JOBID.mutect.callstats.out --coverage_file /mnt/zfs/$JOBID/$JOBID.mutect.coverage.wig#zip /mnt/zfs/$JOBID.mutect.callstats.out.zip /mnt/zfs/$JOBID.mutect.callstats.out#/usr/local/bin/python2.7 /home/cmelton/DynamicDiskCloudSoftware/Worker/GsutilWrapper.py --C 'gsutil|-q|cp|/mnt/zfs/$JOBID.mutect.callstats.out.zip|gs://gbsc-gcp-lab-snyder-users-cmelton/Collaboration/results/$JOBID/$JOBID.$JOBMULT.mutect.callstats.out.zip'#zip /mnt/zfs/$JOBID.mutect.coverage.wig.zip /mnt/zfs/$JOBID.mutect.coverage.wig#/usr/local/bin/python2.7 /home/cmelton/DynamicDiskCloudSoftware/Worker/GsutilWrapper.py --C 'gsutil|-q|cp|/mnt/zfs/$JOBID.mutect.coverage.wig.zip|gs://gbsc-gcp-lab-snyder-users-cmelton/Collaboration/results/$JOBID/$JOBID.$JOBMULT.mutect.coverage.wig.zip'
